{"thi-ap1:0.1":"Theriapadana ","thi-ap1:0.2":"Sumedhavagga ","thi-ap1:0.3":"Sumedhatheriapadana ","thi-ap1:1.1":"Namo tassa Bhagavato Arahato Sammasambuddhassa. ","thi-ap1:2.1":"Atha therikapadanani sunatha—","thi-ap1:3.1":"“Bhagavati konagamane, ","thi-ap1:3.2":"Sangharamamhi navanivesanamhi; ","thi-ap1:3.3":"Sakhiyo tisso janiyo, ","thi-ap1:3.4":"Viharadanam adasimha. ","thi-ap1:4.1":"Dasakkhattum satakkhattum, ","thi-ap1:4.2":"Dasasatakkhattum satananca satakkhattum; ","thi-ap1:4.3":"Devesu upapajjimha, ","thi-ap1:4.4":"Ko vado manuse bhave. ","thi-ap1:5.1":"Deve mahiddhika ahumha, ","thi-ap1:5.2":"manusakamhi ko vado; ","thi-ap1:5.3":"Sattaratanamahesi, ","thi-ap1:5.4":"itthiratanam aham bhavim. ","thi-ap1:6.1":"Idha sancitakusala, ","thi-ap1:6.2":"susamiddhakulappaja; ","thi-ap1:6.3":"Dhananjani ca khema ca, ","thi-ap1:6.4":"ahampi ca tayo jana. ","thi-ap1:7.1":"Aramam sukatam katva, ","thi-ap1:7.2":"sabbavayavamanditam; ","thi-ap1:7.3":"Buddhappamukhasanghassa, ","thi-ap1:7.4":"niyyadetva samodita. ","thi-ap1:8.1":"Yattha yatthupapajjami, ","thi-ap1:8.2":"tassa kammassa vahasa; ","thi-ap1:8.3":"Devesu aggatam patta, ","thi-ap1:8.4":"manussesu tatheva ca. ","thi-ap1:9.1":"Imasmimyeva kappamhi, ","thi-ap1:9.2":"brahmabandhu mahayaso; ","thi-ap1:9.3":"Kassapo nama gottena, ","thi-ap1:9.4":"uppajji vadatam varo. ","thi-ap1:10.1":"Upatthako mahesissa, ","thi-ap1:10.2":"tada asi narissaro; ","thi-ap1:10.3":"Kasiraja kiki nama, ","thi-ap1:10.4":"baranasipuruttame. ","thi-ap1:11.1":"Tassasum satta dhitaro, ","thi-ap1:11.2":"rajakanna sukhedhita; ","thi-ap1:11.3":"Buddhopatthananirata, ","thi-ap1:11.4":"brahmacariyam carimsu ta. ","thi-ap1:12.1":"Tasam sahayika hutva, ","thi-ap1:12.2":"silesu susamahita; ","thi-ap1:12.3":"Datva danani sakkaccam, ","thi-ap1:12.4":"agareva vatam carim. ","thi-ap1:13.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","thi-ap1:13.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","thi-ap1:13.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","thi-ap1:13.4":"tavatimsupaga aham. ","thi-ap1:14.1":"Tato cuta yamamagam, ","thi-ap1:14.2":"tatoham tusitam gata; ","thi-ap1:14.3":"Tato ca nimmanaratim, ","thi-ap1:14.4":"vasavattipuram tato. ","thi-ap1:15.1":"Yattha yatthupapajjami, ","thi-ap1:15.2":"punnakammasamohita; ","thi-ap1:15.3":"Tattha tattheva rajunam, ","thi-ap1:15.4":"mahesittamakarayim. ","thi-ap1:16.1":"Tato cuta manussatte, ","thi-ap1:16.2":"rajunam cakkavattinam; ","thi-ap1:16.3":"Mandalinanca rajunam, ","thi-ap1:16.4":"mahesittamakarayim. ","thi-ap1:17.1":"Sampattimanubhotvana, ","thi-ap1:17.2":"devesu manusesu ca; ","thi-ap1:17.3":"Sabbattha sukhita hutva, ","thi-ap1:17.4":"nekajatisu samsarim. ","thi-ap1:18.1":"So hetu ca so pabhavo, ","thi-ap1:18.2":"Tammulam sasane khamam; ","thi-ap1:18.3":"Pathamam tam samodhanam, ","thi-ap1:18.4":"Tam dhammarataya nibbanam. ","thi-ap1:19.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","thi-ap1:19.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","thi-ap1:19.3":"Nagiva bandhanam chetva, ","thi-ap1:19.4":"viharami anasava. ","thi-ap1:20.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","thi-ap1:20.2":"buddhasetthassa santike; ","thi-ap1:20.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","thi-ap1:20.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","thi-ap1:21.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","thi-ap1:21.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","thi-ap1:21.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","thi-ap1:21.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","thi-ap1:22.1":"Ittham sudam sumedha bhikkhuni ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","thi-ap1:23.1":"Sumedhatheriyapadanam pathamam. "}